TheSoul Publishing is one of the largest digital media publishers in the world, producing entertaining and positive online content for more than 1.5 billion followers around the world. We are the company behind the wildly successful DIY channel 5-Minute Crafts, the inspirational and creative channel Bright Side, and a wide portfolio of other popular channels across YouTube, Facebook, TikTok, Instagram, and more.

