Role Description

Prezi has an ambitious plan to redefine the world of hybrid work through better visual communication. Our ambition is to help people work, learn and collaborate better, and we need an SRE who can help us build and support the platform that will make this happen.

We currently operate a sophisticated Kubernetes landscape on AWS that supports:

Millions of users
20 engineering teams;
100 microservices [python, scala, golang];
1,000 VMs [~10,000+ vCPUs];
20,000 HTTP reqs/sec.

Our ambition is to see these numbers as the launching pad, with big growth ahead. By joining the team at such an exciting time, you will not only have the chance to work on the latest platform technologies, but also help us to define our strategy and evolve our systems to support our next adventure. We are proud of our resilience and availability by design, and we want to ensure we continue to be a trusted partner for our new customers as we grow.

